text: Goundo Diallo (born 19 May 1997) is a Malian basketball player for Sainte Savine Basket and the Malian national team.Afrobasket.com profile She represented Mali at the 2019 Women's Afrobasket.2019 Women's Afrobasket profile ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Forwards (basketball) Category:Malian expatriate basketball people in France Category:Malian women's basketball players
